title: Grateful Dead Live at The Spectrum on 1995-03-18
description:
Set 1

Hell In A Bucket, West L.A. Fadeaway, El Paso*, Ramble On Rose, Just Like Tom Thumb's Blues, Jack A Roe, Promised Land

Set 2

It's All Too Much, Iko Iko, Playin' In The Band-> Uncle John's Band-> Drums-> Space-> The Last Time-> Visions Of Johanna-> One More Saturday Night, E: Rain

* Weir on acoustic, First It's All Too Much
